35:02.600 --> 35:04.202
This is the end for him.

35:07.438 --> 35:08.506
I'm so sorry.

35:22.086 --> 35:23.754
You're still here?

35:25.189 --> 35:27.158
Somebody had to lock up.

35:31.028 --> 35:32.864
Wow, by the looks of this place,

35:32.930 --> 35:36.400
I'd say Operation
"Make GDU the Perfect Family"

35:36.467 --> 35:38.102
appears to be a success.

35:38.169 --> 35:39.937
Yeah, I'm sorry I ducked out.

35:40.004 --> 35:42.173
Kara's dad is dying and...

35:42.240 --> 35:43.608
I just went to be with her.

35:43.674 --> 35:45.877
I apologize for leaving you here.

35:45.943 --> 35:48.045
No, no, that's sweet.

35:48.112 --> 35:50.181
So, everything turned out okay here?

35:50.248 --> 35:52.750
I managed to deal with Dani

35:52.817 --> 35:55.520
and my sanity is still intact.

35:56.320 --> 35:59.223
When did you become this wise sage?

35:59.290 --> 36:01.025
No, seriously, are you a Buddhist?

36:01.092 --> 36:03.160
No, no, I'm not Buddhist.

36:03.227 --> 36:06.230
My mom was bipolar, actually.

36:06.297 --> 36:10.368
She taught me how to have
empathy for people who suffer.

36:10.434 --> 36:12.069
So, you can see somebody like Dani

36:12.136 --> 36:14.472
and have compassion.

36:14.539 --> 36:18.142
Exactly. And the truth is,
it's more for me than them,

36:18.209 --> 36:20.211
'cause it makes my life so much easier.

36:20.278 --> 36:22.380
Mad props to you, girl, cause...

36:22.980 --> 36:25.883
you are wise beyond your years.

36:25.950 --> 36:27.318
Stop.

36:27.385 --> 36:28.920
No, I'm serious.

36:28.986 --> 36:30.655
With people like you leading the way,

36:30.721 --> 36:33.257
future generations might
actually have some hope.

36:33.858 --> 36:35.826
- Preach, queen.
- You know.

36:37.695 --> 36:39.964
Well, I should get going.

36:40.031 --> 36:42.099
You know, hey, Aaliyah.

36:43.935 --> 36:46.637
I hope this doesn't sound weird
or anything, but...

36:47.538 --> 36:49.941
would you wanna hang out some time?

36:50.007 --> 36:52.176
I mean, nothing work related
or anything,

36:52.243 --> 36:53.978
like, not like this, but...

36:55.146 --> 36:58.082
just like, pure,
unadulterated socializing?

36:58.149 --> 37:00.151
I swear I'm not a creeper.

37:00.217 --> 37:01.852
You're being serious right now?

37:01.919 --> 37:02.954
Yeah.

37:03.020 --> 37:06.757
Yes, I would totally love
to hang out with you.

37:06.824 --> 37:08.059
Cool.

37:11.429 --> 37:14.832
No. What are you doing?

37:15.700 --> 37:16.734
Care to join me?

37:21.505 --> 37:24.075
- Would you like to do the honors?
- Sure.

37:24.141 --> 37:25.910
Wait, but first...

37:30.314 --> 37:31.616
Later, sucker.

37:35.953 --> 37:38.255
If I was gonna tell you
how we need to build trust

37:38.322 --> 37:40.191
between our neighborhoods
and the police,

37:40.992 --> 37:42.827
it needed to start right here with me.

37:43.561 --> 37:48.032
When I overcame my drug addiction,
I learned to listen and to trust myself.

37:49.200 --> 37:52.703
It wasn't until then
that I could listen to others.

37:54.438 --> 37:58.609
Listening and understanding,
one person at a time.

37:58.676 --> 38:01.579
That's how we build trust
between ourselves and our community

38:01.646 --> 38:03.347
between our youth and the police,

38:03.414 --> 38:05.149
by really listening to each other.

38:07.852 --> 38:11.155
Yeah, I'll do your color through here.
I think we could do that.

38:12.790 --> 38:14.425
Niecy.

38:14.492 --> 38:16.460
I thought I was clear before.

38:16.527 --> 38:18.396
There's nothing more
I can do to help you.

38:19.463 --> 38:20.631
No, you were clear.

38:21.565 --> 38:24.168
But I have a proposition
for you now, if you will listen.

38:24.235 --> 38:26.070
Girl, five minutes.

38:26.137 --> 38:29.573
It's been hard for me to face up
to the mess that I made of my life.

38:30.141 --> 38:32.443
But I have two kids depending on me now.

38:32.510 --> 38:34.612
You said if something is truly important,

38:34.679 --> 38:39.016
you do the work
and you don't make excuses.

38:39.083 --> 38:40.751
Well, I'm ready to do the work,

38:40.818 --> 38:43.054
and I'm done making excuses.

38:43.587 --> 38:46.424
So, if you will please
give me a second chance,

38:47.158 --> 38:48.626
and give me my booth back.

38:50.428 --> 38:52.196
I don't have any more room, Niecy.

38:52.263 --> 38:53.230
I'm sorry.

38:55.833 --> 38:57.301
All right, well...

38:57.368 --> 38:58.803
I appreciate the opportunity

38:58.869 --> 39:01.739
and thank you for your time, Claudia.

39:03.074 --> 39:04.175
Take care.

39:06.711 --> 39:08.813
Wait, Niecy.

39:10.414 --> 39:14.018
Okay, how about you be
my new shampoo and sweep girl?

39:14.085 --> 39:15.686
You can build up hours in the salon,

39:15.753 --> 39:18.255
and we'll revisit
getting your booth back.

39:18.322 --> 39:20.558
All right. It's a deal. It's a deal.

39:21.292 --> 39:22.259
Great.

39:25.162 --> 39:26.430
You can start today.

39:27.765 --> 39:29.200
Okay.

39:30.735 --> 39:31.769
Thank you.

39:35.272 --> 39:36.707
<i>¿Cómo estás, Lupe?</i>

39:36.774 --> 39:39.143
<i>Muy bien, Miss Mary Jane.
I made coffee for you.</i>

39:39.210 --> 39:42.780
Before I go, I found this
under your couch. It looked important.

39:42.847 --> 39:44.048
<i>Gracias.</i>

39:48.652 --> 39:50.821
Nope, nope. I'm not gonna do it.

39:50.888 --> 39:52.690
I'm gonna leave it there with the others.

39:52.757 --> 39:54.892
I will return it when I can.

39:54.959 --> 39:58.129
I'm not gonna look at you.
I'm not gonna do it.

40:02.266 --> 40:03.501
Damn it.

40:08.806 --> 40:11.175
Justin's worth 30 million dollars?
